what is the area of south san jose known for

South San Jose is known for its high-tech industry, with many major tech companies such as Apple, Google, and Samsung having their headquarters or major offices in the area. It is also known for its diverse culture, with a mix of Asian, Hispanic, and European influences. Additionally, South San Jose has a thriving food scene, with many restaurants and cafes serving a variety of international cuisines.
